<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include("partials/head") %>

<body class="bg-slate-950 min-h-screen text-slate-100">
  <%- include("partials/nav") %>

  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-sky-400 mb-3 ">
            Project Portfolio Gallery
          </p>

          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
            TCSS 460: Project Portfolio Gallery
          </h1>

          <div class="flex flex-col lg:max-w-xl items-center lg:items-start">
            <p class="text-gray-50 mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-5">
                Hi! I'm Landon, an aspiring embedded systems engineer. My recent projects have moved me deeper into hardware by
                designing distributed ESP32-based firmware with FSM architectures and fault recovery, iterating circuit
                designs from schematic through breadboard toward custom PCBs, and integrating sensors into closed-loop
                control systems. I'm most interested in roles where software and hardware work together like embedded
                development, firmware design, hardware validation, and FPGA design.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-row object-fill gap-4 p-2 justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="/gallery" class="text-sky-500 hover:text-sky-400 font-semibold">
              <button
                class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-sky-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-sky-700 transition duration-200 mb-5">
                Explore Gallery
              </button>
            </a>
            <a href="gallery/dead" class="text-sky-500 hover:text-sky-600 font-semibold">
              <button
                class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-sky-500 hover:text-white font-semibold hover:bg-sky-600 transition duration-200 mb-5 border border-sky-500">
                Contact Me
              </button>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="m-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center max-w-md border border-sky-500 rounded-full">
          <img src="images/profile-pic.png" alt="My profile picture." class="rounded-full p-5">
        </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>
